vote.title: An ordinance granting a private license to 2620 Maple Owner, LLC for the use of a total of approximately 169 square feet of land to occupy, maintain, and utilize two electrical conduits, fourteen trees, fourteen uplights, two landscaping blocks and irrigation areas, three trash receptacles, four benches, and a bollard on portions of Maple Avenue and Mahon Street rights-of-way located near its intersection with Mahon Street - Revenue: General Fund $2,000.00 annually and $900.00 one-time fee, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
